{"tid":996260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最有禮貌歹徒　劫車前先還錢包、手機+道歉！","createTime":"2019-01-26T06:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T07:43:37.000Z","uid":32511,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"167d2cc3bcec877a80e36f529f1a16740ad07736","tid":996260,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3861/d3861764.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3861%2Fd3861764.jpg&h=6acf4d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大日前出現一名超有禮貌的歹徒，他在劫車前，竟然還先問車主「後座有小孩嗎？」又再問車主需不需要帶走錢包或手機，之後道了歉，才把車給開走。這一舉甚至被網友笑說，連犯罪都這麼有禮貌！<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n據CBC報導，這起事件發生在加拿大亞伯達省的紅鹿市機場（Red Deer Regional Airport）附近，珍妮佛（Jennifer）於周二開車上班途中，看見一輛小貨卡與校車發生碰撞，而一名疑似是司機的男子站在路上，她趕緊下車查看，想詢問是否需要幫助。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n當珍妮佛靠近一看，發現這名男子用頭巾蒙住半張臉，她發覺不對勁，於是想跑回車內，該男子也跑往車的方向，珍妮佛想要阻止，男子突然從夾克裡掏出一把槍，珍妮佛只好舉手投降。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n然而，在男子劫車時，並沒有忘記「禮儀」，他先是問珍妮佛後座有沒有小孩，又問車上有沒有任何個人物品需要拿走，最後，歹徒把「手機、錢包、便當袋」都還給珍妮佛，還道了歉，之後便開車離去。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n據報導，這起劫車案件似乎是該地區發生一系列劫車案件的一部分，周二有兩名男子用一輛偷來的卡車進行竊盜，其中一名盜賊已經被逮捕，另一名似乎就是此事件的男子。"},{"pid":"e9e81dca3791bdc8bb2517edbbe0bde4074d9cef","tid":996260,"uid":37933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:53:57.000Z","msg":"加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5591698308d89e7158dccaf1313f557fa6d1a2","tid":996260,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a4b0872f8636cea46c340eec9977a836be1f6a","tid":996260,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"左毒"},{"pid":"b967344f5164690dbbda0742e14fda9ad309278f","tid":996260,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"可能係卧底"},{"pid":"5f2083c2e9198089b228a488baf8227d1e88adfb","tid":996260,"uid":26045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:11:36.000Z","msg":"Sorryland<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3224ec99c956e19a2a12ea461d013fedef5bde63","tid":996260,"uid":229806,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:13:47.000Z","msg":"盜亦有道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d07a3f9416980585e9a2d3ca526a5e75ebc31d4","tid":996260,"uid":72749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/26/151509_984c05a5f62d7b15325dc3909d0f594b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F26%2F151509_984c05a5f62d7b15325dc3909d0f594b.jpg&h=04344d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsorry aboot that, eh?"},{"pid":"c80354a8004c43b9de064a2d8db741dfb788ffca","tid":996260,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:41:29.000Z","msg":"Sorry, I am sorry for saying too much sorry, sorry."},{"pid":"c6dd7e58953fa4fda3fa8a2a7cc90154143c26bd","tid":996260,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:43:37.000Z","msg":"膠拿大係sorry大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}